revxrsal.commands.jda

Interface JDAActor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommandActor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseActorJDA

    public interface JDAActor
extends CommandActor
    Represents a JDA CommandActor that executes a command, whether in a private message or a guild.
